# Frontend

- Follow the existing Next.js app router patterns under `frontend/src/app/`.
- Keep domain workspace behavior aligned with `/d/{domainId}/...` routes.
- Use typed props and existing UI/data-fetching patterns before adding new abstractions.
- Do not depend on local generated API data committed to the repo.
- Run `npm run lint`, `npm run typecheck`, and `npm run build` for frontend changes.
- Document new environment variables in `README.md` and `.env.example`.
